<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 The Lamb has overcome
 The Lamb has overcome
 The battle's done
 And the victory is won
 For the Lamb has overcome

[V2]
 No grave could hold him down
 No grave could hold him down
 Up from the ground,
 &quot;He is risen!&quot; was the sound
 No grave could hold him down

[C1]
   Worthy is the Lamb who was slain
   Glory be unto his name

[V3]
 At God's right hand is he
 At God's right hand is he
 Our Perfect Plea,
 How he lives to intercede!
 At God's right hand is he

[V4]
 The table now is spread
 The table now is spread
 This wine and bread
 Broken body and blood shed
 The table now is spread

[V5]
 The day is drawing near
 The day is drawing near
 He shall appear
 And will wipe away each tear
 The day is drawing near</lyrics>
<author>Luke Morton</author>
<title>The Lamb Has Overcome</title>
</song>